单个定量变量的描述性统计

summary(datafile$height) # 对height进行描述性统计
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
##   158.0   163.5   165.5   167.0   169.5   180.0
describe(datafile$height) # 对height进行描述性统计,psych包
##    vars  n mean  sd median trimmed  mad min max range skew kurtosis   se
## X1    1 14  167 6.3  165.5  166.67 5.19 158 180    22  0.5     -0.8 1.68
datafile %>% 
  filter(!is.na(height)) %>%
  summarise(
    n_height = n(),
    min_height = min(height), 
    max_height = max(height),
    mean_height = mean(height), 
    sd_height = sd(height),  
    median_height = median(height), 
    IQR_height = IQR(height), 
    Q1_height = quantile(height,0.25),
